<p class="HELM_exercise">
    Exercise
</p>
<p>
    Express \( \displaystyle{z= {@z@} }\) in Polar form.
</p>
<p>
    \( \displaystyle{z =} \) [[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]][[feedback:prt1]]
</p>
]]></text>
