        <generalfeedback format="html">
            <text><![CDATA[
<p>
    We know that \( z=a+ib= r(\cos{\theta}+i\sin{\theta}) = re^{i\theta}\), where \(\theta=\tan^{-1}(\frac{b}{a})\)and \(r=\sqrt{a^2+b^2}.\)
</p>
<p>
    For \( z\) we have: \( z = {@z@} = {@r@}( \cos{@th@} +i \sin{@th@} ).\)
</p>
<p>
</p>
]]></text>
